text: Sa 'yo Lamang (Only Yours) is a 2010 Filipino religious drama movie directed by Laurice Guillen and starring Lorna Tolentino, Christopher de Leon, Bea Alonzo, Diether Ocampo, Coco Martin, Enchong Dee, Shaina Magdayao. It was distributed by Star Cinema. == Other websites == * Category:2010 drama movies Category:Filipino movies Category:Movies about religion Category:Movies directed by Laurice Guillen
